      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'Survive the night until sunrise.

    The city is losing power. Street
    lights are slowly going dark, and the creatures that roam the darkness grow stronger
    as the light fades.

    Explore the city, restore power to street lights, and
    avoid the monsters that lurk in the shadows.

    If you survive until sunrise,
    you win.

    If the monsters catch you and you lose all your health, the night
    wins.'
